{"tid":2005643,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特情報總監人選視中國最大威脅","createTime":"2020-05-07T08:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T08:42:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8b591c6aebd644d97301d78fb5ee936a827fc4f1","tid":2005643,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T08:41:24.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200507/QRHYFIMPOZXKMXYI4W2BEM6XKA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200507%2FQRHYFIMPOZXKMXYI4W2BEM6XKA%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBder6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=b2430561\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200507%2FQRHYFIMPOZXKMXYI4W2BEM6XKA%2F&h=2e766411\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200507/QRHYFIMPOZXKMXYI4W2BEM6XKA/</a><br />\n<br />\n特情報總監人選視中國最大威脅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200507/large/1588781862_6036.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200507%2Flarge%2F1588781862_6036.jpg&h=7db04008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拉特克里夫前日在參院作供。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普月前提名國會共和黨眾議員拉特克里夫（John Ratcliffe）出任國家情報總監，他前天出席參議院聽證會時指，如獲委任不會讓情報染上政治色彩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n通俄門調查護主受質疑<br />\n<br />\n國家情報總監辦公室掌管全國16個情報機構，去年夏季至今已有七名情報高官離職，總監職位懸空近九個月。惟美國面。。。。。。。。。。。。測特朗普想安插親信出任這要職。<br />\n<br />\n聽證會上他多番被兩黨參議員問及會否不受總統意見左右，尤其在調查武肺能否獨立進行情報工作時，他回應稱「上任後會保持絕對政治中立」，指會專注調查疫情、病毒來源。。。。。。。。。。。最大威脅。<br />\n<br />\n不過他在特朗普捲入的通俄門調查和彈劾案中極力護主，這往績依然。。。。。。。。。。。，九個月前獲特朗普提名，但因缺乏經驗和不受兩黨青睞而退出，月前再獲提名，至今只獲數名共和黨人支持。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/路透社/法新社"},{"pid":"e557ae8e8a0eea9ad908edbbf1d91d216a0c59b8","tid":2005643,"uid":148002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T08:42:16.000Z","msg":"你又做撚嘢Post 全文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}